<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #3b82f6;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #3b82f6;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to GymFitness!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
        <p>We're excited to have you join GymFitness! Your journey to better fitness tracking starts now.</p>
        <p>With your new account, you can:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Track all your gym workouts</li>
          <li>Set and monitor fitness goals</li>
          <li>See your progress over time</li>
          <li>Stay motivated on your fitness journey</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To get started, log in to your account and set up your first fitness goal or log your first workout.</p>
        <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="button">Go to GymFitness</a>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>The GymFitness Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© <%= Date.today.year %> GymFitness. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You're receiving this email because you signed up for GymFitness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>